      "title": "Sri Lanka hikes Kerosene prices",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The price of Kerosene has been increased to Rs. 340/- per litre by the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation.",
        "Accordingly, the price of Kerosene has increased by Rs 253/- per litre.",
        "The price revision will be in effect from midnight today (21).",
        "World Bank impose strict regulations for fertilizer imports \u2013 Report"
